3:47 Nowshin Nowher Orpi, if you ever see this, please know that I’ve loved you since the very first day I saw you at the university. That moment changed something in me forever. This love will live on even beyond my last breath.

Even if destiny never lets me have you in my life, I’ll still find peace in your happiness — whether it’s with me or with someone else.
